sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant API
  participant AuthService
  participant ControlDB
  User->>API: signup/login
  API->>AuthService: validate/hash/verify
  AuthService->>ControlDB: user/session/workspace
  ControlDB-->>AuthService: session token hash
  API-->>User: token-bearing response
  User->>API: Authorization header
  API->>AuthService: resolveSession
